// |  TAB |  Q  |  W  |  E  |  R  |  T  |                                  |  Y  |   U  |  I  |  O  |  P  |   \  |
// | SHFT |  A  |  S  |D/ViD|F/SYM|  G  |                                  |  H  |   J  |  K  |  L  |  ;  |   '  |
// | CTRL |  Z  |  X  |  C  |  V  |  B  |                                  |  N  |   M  |  ,  |  .  |  /  | ALTTB|
// |  ESC | WIN | ALT | CAPW| 10K |     | BKSP | | DEL |      | RET | SPAC |     | ARRBR| CAP | FUN | MACR| GAME |
                        bindings = <
    &kp TAB     &kp Q       &kp W       &kp E     &kp R    &kp T                                             &kp Y    &kp U    &kp I        &kp O      &kp P        &kp BSLH
    &kp LSHFT   &kp A       &kp S       &lt 2 D   &lt 3 F  &kp G                                             &kp H    &kp J    &kp K        &kp L      &kp SEMI     &kp SQT
    &kp LCTRL   &kp Z       &kp X       &kp C     &kp V    &kp B                                             &kp N    &kp M    &kp COMMA    &kp DOT    &kp FSLH     &mt LA(TAB) LA(LC(TAB))
    &kp ESC     &kp LGUI    &kp LALT    &none     &mo 4            &kp BSPC  &kp DEL    &kp RET  &kp SPACE            &mo 1    &caps_word   &sl 5      &none        &none
                        >;
                };

